<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='590445' id='t-590445'>And with that in mind,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='592369' id='t-592369'>I'd like to say a few words about traditional college grading.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='596973' id='t-596973'>I'm sick of it.</span>
